HONG KONG , November 26 -LRB- Xinhua -RRB- -- The People 's Liberation Army -LRB- PLA -RRB- Garrison in the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region -LRB- HKSAR -RRB- started a new normal troop rotation early Friday morning .
The rotation is being carried out in accordance with the Garrison Law of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region which stipulates a personnel rotation system for garrison troops .
This is the second normal troop rotation of the PLA Hong Kong Garrison since it assumed Hong Kong 's defense responsibility on July 1 , 1997 .
It features a routine troop rotation in units of the PLA army , navy and air force .
The rotation started from the early morning Friday and is scheduled to end at noon .
